thread.title: Man killed in car-semi collision on Circle Dr.
thread.title_full: Man killed in car-semi collision on Circle Dr.

author: cbc
title: Man killed in car-semi collision on Circle Dr.
text:
A 34-year-old man who was hospitalized after a car-semi collision in Saskatoon has died of his injuries.
The crash happened Wednesday evening on Circle Drive at Attridge Drive.
The man's compact car collided head-on with the semi. The crash shut down a section of Circle Drive while collision analysts pieced together what happened.
Police are not yet releasing the victim's name.
